# First-join: teleport to spawn world + give the Server Wiki book.
# NeoEssentials spawnOnJoin is unreliable, so we handle it here via the root advancement (triggers once on first tick).
execute in multiworld:spawn run tp @s -247.5 84.0 184.5 179.25 -4.2
give @s minecraft:written_book[minecraft:written_book_content={title:"Server Wiki",author:"Server",pages:['{"text":"§lWelcome!§r\\n\\n• /quests\\n• /spawn\\n• /sethome  /home\\n• /tpa <player>\\n• /money  /pay\\n• #3 = post slot 3 mon in chat"}','{"text":"§lHealing§r\\n\\n• Right-click a Pokémon with a carrot → +30 HP\\n\\n• Poké Healer block: full party heal + revive (charges market price for missing carrots)"}','{"text":"§lLevel Cap§r\\n\\nCap = 20 + 5 per mainline gym beaten. Max 70 at gym 10. Elite Four complete = uncapped.\\n\\n• Wild spawns clamp near your cap (level + form).\\n\\n• Only OFFICIAL gym fights downlevel your team. Wild + non-gym trainer battles use your full strength."}','{"text":"§lGyms§r\\n\\n• Battle gyms of increasing difficulty in spawn to raise your level cap, gain rewards, and progress through the story!\\n\\n• 18 gyms + Elite 4\\n\\n• Lootballs found while exploring give pokemon EXP (in addition to battles)"}','{"text":"§lMarket§r\\n\\n• /buy <item> [qty]\\n• /sell <item> [qty]\\n• /prices  /prices <item>\\n\\nDynamic pricing — stock changes with every trade."}','{"text":"§lGacha§r\\n\\n• Lootbox keys from daily login, ranked battles, gym progress + milestones\\n\\n• /gacha — view box tables\\n\\n• Gacha eggs: 2 perfect IVs, often hidden abilities!"}','{"text":"§lRanked PvP§r\\n\\n• /challenge <player>\\n• /accept  /decline\\n• /stats [player]\\n• /ranked leaderboard\\n\\nPvP earns prizes + money. Max 1 legendary in ranked + tournaments."}','{"text":"§lFarms & Trade§r\\n\\n• Create farms or factories to make and sell valuable items on the stock market. Sell too much and the market will crash.\\n\\n• Use the Cobbleworkers mod to employ your pokemon for farming, fishing, brewing, and more!\\ndocs.accieo.com/cobbleworkers/"}','{"text":"§lMinecolony§r\\n\\n• Build a minecolony with friends to grow your own town. Collect materials to expand and construct more buildings.\\n\\n• Wild pokemon battles near your town give boosted EXP.\\n\\n• Invite friends — share their EXP from wild battles + exploration while both online."}','{"text":"§lMore§r\\n\\n• Streak mechanic: catch 10 gastly in a row → higher shiny rate + IVs\\n\\n• Follow long and difficult quests to obtain your favorite legendaries"}']}] 1
